t MS"/></a:rPr></a:br><a:r><a:rPr i="1" lang="en-US" sz="981"><a:solidFill><a:schemeClr val="dk1"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:ea typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:cs typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:sym typeface="Trebuchet MS"/></a:rPr><a:t>The event provided a unique platform to exchange ideas, showcase innovation, and strengthen partnerships in the renewable energy sector. I have been impressed by the knowledge shared by regulators, investors, and startups here. With that strong foundation, I am confident that India is going to accelerate rapidly in biogas and bioenergy. The conference has been fantastic — a place where so many people have come together to discuss and showcase the best technology available in India.&quot;</a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr i="1" sz="981"><a:solidFill><a:schemeClr val="dk1"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:ea typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:cs typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:sym typeface="Trebuchet MS"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p></p:txBody></p:sp><p:grpSp><p:nvGrpSpPr><p:cNvPr id="519" name="Google Shape;519;g379e1930da7_0_213"/><p:cNvGrpSpPr/><p:nvPr/></p:nvGrpSpPr><p:grpSpPr><a:xfrm><a:off x="278700" y="1946125"/><a:ext cx="2327400" cy="2797800"/><a:chOff x="551050" y="1473000"/><a:chExt cx="2327400" cy="2797800"/></a:xfrm></p:grpSpPr><p:sp><p:nvSpPr><p:cNvPr id="520" name="Google Shape;520;g379e1930da7_0_213"/><p:cNvSpPr txBox="1"/><p:nvPr/></p:nvSpPr><p:spPr><a:xfrm><a:off x="551050" y="3429000"/><a:ext cx="2327400" cy="841800"/></a:xfrm><a:prstGeom prst="rect"><a:avLst/></a:prstGeom><a:noFill/><a:ln><a:noFill/></a:ln></p:spPr><p:txBody><a:bodyPr anchorCtr="0" anchor="t" bIns="81175" lIns="81175" spcFirstLastPara="1" rIns="81175" wrap="square" tIns="81175"><a:noAutofit/></a:bodyPr><a:lstStyle/><a:p><a:pPr indent="0" lvl="0" marL="0" rtl="0" algn="ctr"><a:spcBef><a:spcPts val="0"/></a:spcBef><a:spcAft><a:spcPts val="0"/></a:spcAft><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr b="1" lang="en-US" sz="1200"><a:solidFill><a:schemeClr val=